#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kubrick; is a game based on the <trademark>Rubik's Cube</trademark> puzzle. "
"The cube sizes range from 2x2x2 up to 6x6x6, or you can play with irregular "
"<quote>bricks</quote> such as 5x3x2 or <quote>mats</quote> such as 6x4x1 or "
"2x2x1. The game has a selection of puzzles at several levels of difficulty, "
"as well as demos of pretty patterns and solution moves, or you can make up "
"your own puzzles ..."
msgstr ""
"&kubrick; je igra, ki temelji na uganki <trademark>Rubikova kocka</"
"trademark>. Velikosti kock segajo od 2x2x2 do 6x6x6 ali pa se lahko igrate z "
"nepravilnimi <quote>kvadri</quote>, kot je 5x3x2, ali <quote>podlogami</"
"quote>, kot sta 6x4x1 ali 2x2x1. Igra ima izbor ugank na več težavnostnih "
"ravneh, pa tudi predstavitve lepih vzorcev in potez rešitev, lahko pa si "
"izmislite svoje uganke ..."

